nodes.text: Taneka Shirru was a female Sith Saber who was native to the planet of Kesh. Shirru was part of the Lost Tribe of Sith infiltration team that took up residence in the newly-abandoned Jedi Temple on Coruscant, under orders of Grand Lord Darish Vol. She was killed by an "unknown lifeform" within the lower corridors of the Jedi temple.
